LidoAdapter_Integration_Concrete_Test::stake
└── when caller not SablierBob
   └── it should revert

LidoAdapter_Integration_Concrete_Test::unstakeFullAmount
└── when caller not SablierBob
   └── it should revert

LidoAdapter_Integration_Concrete_Test::calculateAmountToTransferWithYield
├── given no yield bearing token balance
│  └── it should return zero
└── given yield token balance not zero
   └── given not unstaked
      └── it should return zero

LidoAdapter_Integration_Concrete_Test::supportsInterface
├── when querying ISablierBobAdapter interface
│  └── it should return true
├── when querying ISablierLidoAdapter interface
│  └── it should return true
├── when querying IERC165 interface
│  └── it should return true
└── when querying invalid interface
   └── it should return false

LidoAdapter_Integration_Concrete_Test::getVaultYieldFee
├── given no fee changes after creation
│  └── it should return the snapshotted fee
└── given global fee changed after creation
   └── it should return the original snapshotted fee
